                     <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;padding-top: 80px;padding-right: 40px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 30px;"><span style="line-height:1.5;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Hello {{{ServiceAppointment.Contact_Name__c}}},&nbsp;</span></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">To confirm a date for the next appointment for the pool start-up, a payment must be done.<br /> Once the payment is complet, it takes approximately 1 to 3 days to receive confirmation for the following appointment by email. We recommend making the payment quickly to prevent a delay in the project.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">A balance of&nbsp;{{{ServiceAppointment.Order_Amount_Due__c}}}&nbsp;must be paid.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">The payment can be made online (customer access plateform) and/or cash/debit/credit card in any Trevi store.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">You can also create Trevi as a payee in order to pay your balance (payee : Trevi Mirabel, Account number : customer number).&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><a href="https://espaceclient.trevi.com/detaillants/papeterie/CORPO-22_Proc%C3%A9dure%20de%20paiement%20en%20ligne%20-(bilingue).pdf?v=2023"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><strong>Payment procedure</strong></span></span></a><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">&nbsp;<br /><br /> &nbsp;<br /> We invite you to consult your customer area on the Trevi website </span></span><a href="http://www.trevi.com/"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">www.trevi.com</span></span></a>&nbsp;<span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">where you will find a lot of information as well as a FAQ.&nbsp;<br /><br /> Here is the link to access the work description and requirements where you will find all the information concerning the steps of your project : </span></span><a href="https://espaceclient.trevi.com/detaillants/papeterie/pour_bon_suivi_lors_installation_cr_eng.pdf?v=20240805"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">Work desccription and requirements</span></span></a>.<span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br /><br /> Our stores also offer free maintenance courses, here is the link to register : </span></span><a href="http://www.trevi.com/"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">In-store courses</span></span></a><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:12px;">.<br /><br /><br /> Cordially.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br /> Your inground pool Delivery/Installation Department Team&nbsp;<br /> Phone: 514-228-7384 &nbsp;<br /> Delivery poste: 2106&nbsp;<br /> Installation poste: 2100&nbsp;<br /> Email: creusee@trevi.ca &nbsp;</span></span></span></td>
